{"tid":1354550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航空界周五機場集會　大家一齊聲援佢地啦！！","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T01:13:09.000Z","uid":265019,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eb359a93a2d1992f7e814cdddebf23c5b41b261b","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"周日（21日）有示威者包圍中聯辦後於上環與警方爆發衝突，同日元朗有大批白衣人於西鐵站內襲擊記者及市民。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一班航空界職員將於周五（26日）於機場接機大堂集會，要求政府起訴施襲者，並成立獨立調查委員會徹查警方暴力行為。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n集會將於周五下午 1 時開始，參與者將向遊客分享一系列事件的新聞、影片等，並收集公眾請願書表達對政府的不滿。發起人之一的航空界員工向《立場新聞》表示，今次集會由航空界職員自發，希望政府盡快回應 5 大訴求，今次是和平集會，正申請不反對通知書，公民黨議員譚文豪及職工盟有提供協助，但緊守無大台原則，職工盟不會帶領集會，所有安排由參與者自發。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他強調，今次行動不涉及機管局、任何航空公司、工會，亦非罷工，不是要令機場癱瘓，是希望引起各方關注。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n他們的聲明批評，警方於六月及七月期間對抗爭者採取不恰當暴力，包括周日晚上於上環再次向抗爭者發射橡膠子彈及布袋彈，同時港府和警方無視元朗不法之徒隨機襲擊市民，更有大量報告證明報案熱線的工作人員對市民不屑一顧、元朗及天水圍警署早早關起大閘、警方於事件發生一小時後才到場、警察對手持武器走過的施襲者並沒有採取任何行動。<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱對香港的治安感到憂心，呼籲機場同業參與集會，並要求香港政府立即採取行動，起訴施襲者並成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n各位，我地一齊用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己的方式</span></span>支持佢地啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n大家記得，大會話，無意令<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場癱瘓</span></span></strong>。唔好亂來呀！！"},{"pid":"bed40d9d9a6ff0bd3572226893bf62867d3a534d","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e7f89d5a483d5b704fba8c131f8caaeed9f81e","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e98a59c475f60e0bec3eef88fb9c5e664c50639","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a78f6a45b197bf16a6e2d5e4f844356e629192","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed6b53f267038f3b347556fa6360336a816ef6d","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78e303b55dd80a2e0174774dedfed1b4fc3e2c6","tid":1354550,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd7dff11e5f5284e92df8836f30c90f0c7772bc","tid":1354550,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"在接機大堂，唔易有不反對通知書"},{"pid":"7f7e2ea1c3007956a8b7263710cff9d1b1f090b0","tid":1354550,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4d313b38c780a416a76b8c9ba556d8426e82c074","tid":1354550,"uid":